snippet.title: Garden Witch Life - Launch Trailer - Out Now!
snippet.description:
Garden Witch Life is now available on PC (Steam, Epic Games Store), Nintendo Switch, PS5 and Xbox Series X/S

You are a little witch from the big city who has just lost their job. Life didn’t go as you expected but now you can start anew on a tiny island full of possibilities! Grow your own magical garden, decorate your ancient tree house, care for cute creatures, and make friends along the way. Cook delicious new recipes using homegrown ingredients and be part of a wonderful community working together to make it thrive!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1240450
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/garden-witch-life-switch
Playstation 5: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10009822
Xbox Series X/S: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/garden-witch-life/9nzhfp0sbqnm
Epic Store: https://store.epicgames.com/p/garden-witch-life-f4c4b3

Website: https://gardenwitchlife.com/
All links: https://gardenwitchlife.com/links/

Discord: https://discord.com/invite/9b8nNxaj5N
Twitter: https://twitter.com/freetime_studio
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/freetimestudio/
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@freetimestudio
